BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:NEJWtb_rqKT3deWTRbBOi
SUMMARY:Paella Pop-up at a/stir
DTSTAMP:20260411T040854Z
DTSTART:20260421T010000Z
DESCRIPTION:You know us \\(or maybe you don't\\). We are obssessed with Nor
	thern Mediterranean cuisine. What is more quintessential than Paella when 
	it comes to Northern Mediterranean? \\(Well\, a few other dishes but paell
	a is certainly one of them\\). So\, join us for a very limited pop-up for 
	a seafood paella pop-up at a/stir. The ONLY option for dinner is\, you gue
	ssed it\, paella. What is in it? This one will feature smoked chicken thig
	hs\, mussels\, shrimp and chorizo \\(no\, we won't forget the saffron\, on
	ion and the bell peppers\\). No vegan or vegetarian options this time arou
	nd. \n\nWhat else comes with it? A glass of Spanish wine - white or red\, 
	your choice. \n\nAnything else? Well\, if you so choose\, you will be able
	 to order a side salad and a basque cheesecake as dessert \\(neither are i
	ncluded in price\, and both in very limited quantities\\). \n\nSeatings at
	 6pm\, 7pm or 8pm. Choose carefully. :-\\)\n\nPrice? $50/person\, inclusiv
	e of taxes and gratuity. Includes a generous portion of paella and a 5 oz 
	glass of delicious Spanish wine. Salad and Basque cheesecake optionally av
	ailable at the restaurant at time of dinner.\n\nFINE PRINT\n\nSince this i
	s a pop-up\, we cannot make any accomodations and substitutions with food 
	content. There will NOT be any other regular menu items on the day of serv
	ice - this is a pop-up for PAELLA only.\n\nNot a drinker? Don't wanna pay 
	for the wine? Consider joining us at another pop-up event. Since this is s
	uch a limited and narrow scope engagement\, we are not in a position to ac
	comodate requests.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/paella
	-pop-up-at-a-stir/18529146/2026-04-20T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drink
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/paella-pop-up-at-a-stir/1
	8529146/2026-04-20T00
LOCATION:a/stir\, 818 E Pike St\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-food
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Food & Drink
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
